7"></a><a href="#_ftnref7">[7]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> “Joint Israeli-Palestinian Poll,” </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Harry S. Truman Research Institute for the Advancement of Peace</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> and</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Palestinian Center for Policy and Survey Research</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> December 2013</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">.</span></p></body></html>